MTIO -- Magtape i/o.  This directory contains the FIO device driver for the
magtape devices plus MTOPEN (used to open a magtape device and hook it to
FIO) plus a few other routines.  See ./doc for additional info.

--------------------------
Revisions

16-Jul-85 dct
	Changed the "drive" argument to ZZOPMT and ZZRWMT from an integer to
	a character string.  Tweaked the interface to permit use with the
	kernel server (but it will still all work if the kernel server is
	not used).
